data.description:
Don't miss the chance to cherish every moment in this gem! Welcoming you with warmth and charm, this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers an inviting open concept design that seamlessly integrates the kitchen, living, and dining areas. Step onto trendy gray laminate flooring that graces the main living spaces, creating a modern and cohesive aesthetic.

The allure continues into the primary bedroom, where you'll discover a haven of comfort featuring a stunning en suite with his-and-her sinks, a beautifully tiled shower, and a generously sized walk-in closet. Picture cozy evenings by the electric fireplace, the living room becoming the heart of the home.

Beyond the interior, an oversized 3-car garage not only provides ample parking space but also includes a built-in storm shelter, ensuring safety during unexpected weather events. Nestled on an expansive lot, this well maintained home promises longevity and a sense of space.

Seize the opportunity to make this inviting abode yours!  An ideal location near highway and turnpike access in a picturesque neighborhood!  This is a rare find and will not last long! Get ready to schedule your private tour soon.  Realtor and buyer are encouraged to verify all information.
